\end_inset

.
 
\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Internationally, the introduction of the tax was noted as well, because
 some countries, especially the UK, had public discussions on the topic
 as obesity continues to be a serious threat to public health.
\begin_inset Foot
