\end_inset

.
 
\end_layout

\end_inset

 According to the National Obesity Forum in the UK, 70% of the British populatio
n would be obese in 2050 if nothing is done to prevent it.
\begin_inset Foot
status collapsed

\begin_layout Plain Layout
