\end_inset

.
 
\end_layout

\end_inset

 Other countries imposed similar taxes such as Hungary that put a tax on
 foods with high fat, salt and sugar content.
\begin_inset Foot
status collapsed

\begin_layout Plain Layout
Catherine Cheney, ‘Battling the Couch Potatoes: Hungary Introduces “Fat
 Tax”’, Spiegel Online, 1 September 2011, 
\begin_inset CommandInset href
