.
 
\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
In November 2012, a new centre-left government and its supporting party
 agreed on abolishing the tax.
 The reasons presented were that the tax was the source of considerable
 administrative burdens and that it was the cause of social skewness.
 The tax was formally abolished from 1 January 2013.
\begin_inset Foot
